channel.title: Weirdest Problem
channel.description:
Okay so I have my server and client and it is online, but my server is only getting like 2 or 3 players online ever. Now I know what you are thinking, but my server has over 102 downloads and I was just like wtf?! how is this happening. so I went to my friends house and tried to login from his comp. and it kept getting an error saying
"error connecting to server" or "No response from server"
How could is get no response when the account isn't even created yet? SO the weird question is, why can some players connect but most other players cannot? and is there any possible chance to fix this. I am willing to pay $$$ for to who ever can fully 100% fix this problem!
